children.name: WITH "key_data_stats" AS (SELECT DISTINCT http_server_request.http_server_request ->> 'request_method'::text AS "request_method", http_server_request.http_server_request ->> 'normalized_path_info'::text AS "path_info" FROM "users_orgs", "scenarios", LATERAL jsonb_to_recordset(COALESCE(scenarios.events_http_server_requests, '[]'::jsonb)) http_server_request(id integer, http_server_request jsonb) WHERE (("scenarios"."org_id" = "users_orgs"."org_id") AND ("user_id" = 15))) SELECT count(*) AS "num_distinct" FROM "key_data_stats" LIMIT 1
